    but check versions!
  * better support for standardized colored output
  * proper getopt support
  * support convenient building from source (get deps, invoke sbcl)
  * website
  * proper help
  * actively support versioned deps
  * lightbg color scheme
  * add arch=i686 automatically, x86_64 after asking
  * support generic restarts/cerror
      exit
      continue/ignore
      sync-database

